lyrics:
Khawvelah Pathianin,
Hmun tinreng a awh kim;
Amah a hnai reng fo,
Thlarau ch ak lote tan;
A aw hriat phakin a hnai reng,
Ka tan a tha Pathian hnaih chu.
Lalpa a pangngai fo,
Khawvel buainaah pawh;
Mihring danglam mah se,
Ani a thuhmun fo;
Buaina tui fawna suanglungpui,
Ka tan a tha Pathian hnaih chu.
Hausakna chhui rual loh,
A hausakna phalin;
A thatna tawp lovin,
Thil nung tinreng a chawm;
A hmangaih far khat tuipui ang,
Ka tan a tha Pathian hnaih chu.
